ðŸš« No Lat/Long? No Problem.

You donâ€™t need maps to get heatmap value. The render heatmap in Sentinel is basically a 2D matrix visualizerâ€”use it to display frequency, volume, or abnormal access relationships between two axes. That could be:

Account â†” Host

